<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{NAME}} 模块</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #f0f0f0);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }
        .info {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .info p {
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        .success {
            color: #4ade80;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        .fs-sm {
            font-size: 0.9rem !important;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; }
        }
        .status {
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        a {
          text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>✨ {{NAME}} 模块 ✨</h1>
        <div class="success">✓ 运行正常</div>
        <div class="info">
            <p>➤ 1、当前模块: {{NAME}}</p>
            <p>➤ 2、命名空间: {{MODULE_NAMESPACE}}</p>
            <p>➤ 3、操作指南: {{ config('modules.namespace', 'Modules') }}/UserGuide.md </p>
            <p>➤ 4、多模块包：<a href="https://packagist.org/packages/zxf/modules" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><code class="success fs-sm">composer require zxf/modules</code></a></p>
            <p>➤ 5、欢迎Star：<a href="https://github.com/zhaoxianfang/modules" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="success fs-sm">GitHub</a>、<a href="https://gitee.com/zhaoxianfang/modules" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="success fs-sm">Gitee</a> </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>不是因为看到希望才坚持，而是坚持了才看到希望。🍃</p>
            <p>Powered by <span>{{ config('app.name', 'Laravel') }}</span></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

